  "display_name": "Legal Education and Practice Innovations",
  "description": "This cluster of papers explores the impact of legal education on society, professionals, and access to justice. It delves into topics such as the health impacts of welfare rights advice, lawyer wellbeing, professionalism, ethical codes, and social exclusion. Additionally, it investigates civil justice problems and the role of clinical legal education in addressing societal issues.",
